            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, separate 6<strong> outer lettuce leaves </strong>per person,<strong> </strong>wash and dry them well with kitchen paper then shred the <strong>inner core[s]</strong> finely</p><p>Chop your <strong>coriander</strong> finely, including the stalks</p><p>Strip your <strong>mint leaves</strong> from their stems and chop them finely</p><p>Grate your <strong>carrot[s]<span class=\"text-danger\"> </span></strong>and cut your <strong>lime[s]</strong> in half</p><p>Cut<strong> half </strong>the <strong>lime[s]</strong> into wedges</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1886.-step-5-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1886.-step-5-x400.jpg",
