            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1886.-step-5-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine your <strong>creamy</strong> <strong>peanut butter</strong>, <strong>chilli relish</strong>, 1 tsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tsp]<strong> </span>sugar </strong>and 3 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[4 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[5 tbsp]</span> <strong>boiled water </strong>in a small bowl</p><p>Add your <strong>soy sauce</strong> and the juice of<strong> half</strong> the <strong>remaining lime</strong> and stir it all together – this is your <strong>satay sauce</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1886.-step-6-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
