            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Divide the <strong>chicken satay noodle filling</strong> between the <strong>lettuce leaves</strong></p><p>Garnish with your<strong> sesame seeds </strong>and a <strong>lime wedge</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
